data.description: Looking for the home that is ready to move in? Here it is with all new floors, furnace was replace in early 2023. New stove, fridge, washer and dryer all included. Septic was cleaned out and inspected in late 2022. Includes a 1.5 car attached garage and the bonus detached 1 car garage? This all sits on just over a half acre and is ready for you to move in.
